{
  "stem": "12810.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I think we go through that out of each other there because he don't come to the synagogue anymore, and we have-- my mother-- my mother's mother bought us a seat-- you know how it is in a synagogue, you have to buy a seat.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then because he left the Jewish fate, they take away the seat what my mother's mother bought.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my brother, it was just before bar mitzvah.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my mother said, how you can take it away?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Here is the boy who is a bar mitzvah and he needs the seat.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they take it away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So, again, we were hurt because of my father.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So all my life he was not so, how I say it to you, not so close.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Did he support the family financially or he didn't need to?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He has to because the law tell him, but he didn't.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he-- first of all, he don't want to divorce my mother.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's always said to my mother, you are my wife, she is only my girlfriend.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my mother said, I don't want to eat a cherry in the same plate with anybody.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was the two different type of characters-- my mother and my father.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he did divorce her?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But my grandmother always said to me-- to us-- cost us a fortune.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One house went to the lawyers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because for two years, he don't want to divorce.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But my grandmother let my mother swear she will never go back to him because of his nature.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But my mother loved him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Still, when we went to the ghetto, my father sent the courier, his trucks and things to take the furnishings and everything.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And after that many years, I see my mother and father together.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
